{"id": "chos026", "name": "Cam_Riverside_702_09_18_1", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Riverside"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon'sBike_Off", "Engines Off"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "We're here.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "We don't need to use the transceivers here?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "There's no one here, no need for that. On top of that, I can pretty much guess where you were standing at the time...\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Yeah, it's right there.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-A.I.]"], "content": "<i>Rewind Starts.</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "So you really do come here by yourself for no reason...?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Yes. I come here to repent myself for leaving without ever saying \"Sorry\" to you...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[</blockquote>< Flashback </blockquote><]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2602"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Here's all the evidence. Is this the \"secret\" that you've been unable to tell me all this time...?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "I...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... I should have let him die...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon... I really don't know about this...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You've been helping him all this time, right?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "We... this is the only way for us to live...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "He's a murderer!!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"4.2\">HE'S MY FATHER!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Even if he is, he is just a criminal to me now. For the things that he has done... I will not allow him to escape the law!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Then what about me? Am I also just a criminal to you now?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "You can't accept this, can you? The real me...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n... I don't...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<i>*Bawls*</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2603"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Riverside"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon'sBike_Off", "エンジンを切る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "降りろ。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "トランシーバ使わなくていいの？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ここは誰もいないからいい。\nそれに聞かなくてもお前がどこら辺にいたのかなんて、大体予想つくしな。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "そう、そこ。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-A.I.]"], "content": "<i>リワインド開始</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "本当にひとりで来てたのか。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うん。あの時「ごめんなさい」も言えずにいなくなったことを懺悔しに来てた……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[</blockquote><巻き戻し</blockquote><]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2602"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "証拠はここにある。これが、ずっと言えなかった「秘密」か……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "私……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……俺…あの時…あのまま、あいつを死なせればよかった……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……あたし、ほんとに知らなかった……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ずっと協力してきたんだろ？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あたしたちは…生きるためにこうするしかなかった……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あいつは殺人犯だ！！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"4.2\">あたしの父さんだよ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……だとしても、今の俺にとってはただの犯罪者だ。\nあいつがやってきたことを……見逃すわけにはいかない！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……じゃあ、あたしは？\nあたしも今のSimonにとっては、ただの犯罪者？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "やっぱり、本当のあたしを受け入れるなんて無理だったんだね……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n……俺には……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うっ！うぅ……！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2603"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Riverside"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon'sBike_Off", "引擎熄火"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "下車吧。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "這邊不用對講機了？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這裡沒人，不用了，而且我大概猜得到妳在哪個位置……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "對，就是那邊。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-A.I.]"], "content": "<i>回溯開始。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳還真的會沒事一個人跑來啊……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯，來這裡懺悔自己當初「對不起」都沒說就離開了……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[</blockquote><倒轉</blockquote><]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2602"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "證據都在這裡了，這就是妳一直沒有跟我說的「祕密」嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我應該讓他死的……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……我真的不知道這件事……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳一直以來都在幫他對吧？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我們……只能靠這種方式生活……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "他是個殺人犯啊！！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"4.2\">他是我爸！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……就算是，他現在對我來說只是個罪犯。\n他做的那些事……我不會讓他逍遙法外！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……那我呢？我現在對你來說也只是個罪犯？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你果然不能接受吧？真正的我……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n……我不……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗚嗚！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2603"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Riverside"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon'sBike_Off", "시동을 끈다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "내리자.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "여기선 무전기 쓸 필요 없겠지?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "응. 여긴 아무도 없으니깐. 그리고 내 예상이 맞는다면, 네가 서 있던 위치는.....\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "응. 바로 저기야.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-A.I.]"], "content": "<i>역추적 시작</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "너 정말로 여기에 아무 이유 없이 혼자 왔었던 거지……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "응. 여기에서 「미안하다」라는 사과 한마디 없이 이별했던 것을 후회하곤 했거든....\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[</blockquote><되감기</blockquote><]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2602"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "모든 증거가 여기에 있어. 이것이 네가 내게 말했던 「비밀」이라는 거야……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "난……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": ".... 그냥 죽도록 내버려 뒀어야 했어...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon…… 난 진짜로 몰랐어....\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "넌 계속 그 사람을 도와 왔던 거겠지? 내 말이 맞아? \n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "우린…… 그런 생활에 의존할 수밖에 없는 상황이었....\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그 사람은 살인자야!!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"4.2\">그 사람은 우리 아빠라고!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……지금 나한테는 그저 범죄자일 뿐. 무조건 법의 심판을 받도록 하겠어.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……그럼 나는? 그럼 나도 이제 너한테 그냥 범죄자일 뿐인 거야?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "역시 받아들일 수 없는 거지? 나의 진짜 모습을....\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……!\n……그건……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "흑!..흐윽.....!\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2603"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Riverside"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon'sBike_Off", "引擎熄火"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "下車吧。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "這邊不用對講機了？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這裡沒人，不用了，而且我大概猜得到妳在哪個位置……\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "對，就是那邊。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon-A.I.]"], "content": "<i>回溯開始。</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳還真的會沒事一個人跑來啊……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯，來這裡懺悔自己當初「對不起」都沒說就離開了……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[</blockquote><倒轉</blockquote><]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2602"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "證據都在這裡了，這就是妳一直沒有跟我說的「祕密」嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation