, "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳还真的会没事一个人跑来啊……？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯，来这里忏悔自己当初「对不起」都没说就离开了……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[</blockquote><倒转</blockquote><]</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2602"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "证据都在这里了，这就是妳一直没有跟我说的「秘密」吗……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我应该让他死的……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……我真的不知道这件事……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳一直以来都在帮他对吧？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我们……只能靠这种方式生活……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "他是个杀人犯啊！ ！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"4.2\">他是我爸！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……就算是，他现在对我来说只是个罪犯。\n他做的那些事……我不会让他逍遥法外！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……那我呢？我现在对你来说也只是个罪犯？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你果然不能接受吧？真正的我……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n……我不……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "呜呜！\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2603"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>"}]]}